nter; font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-word;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 40px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 40px;\"><strong><code spellcheck=\"false\" data-bee-type=\"mergetag\" data-bee-code=\"\" data-bee-name=\"Event Name\">{{event.name}}</code>&nbsp;</strong><code spellcheck=\"false\" data-bee-type=\"mergetag\" data-bee-code=\"\" data-bee-name=\"First name\">&nbsp;</code>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-word;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-word;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-word;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px;\">Our company has organized this event to bring together industry leaders, business professionals, and entrepreneurs to network and exchange ideas. It is an opportunity to learn from each other and establish business relationships that can help you take your business to the next level. Please find the event details below:</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-word;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-word;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-word;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px;\">Event: {{ev<em>ent.name}} <br></em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; w